         <abstract>
            <p>The paper develops a concept of a multi-user infotainment system , taking its application in a tourist bus as an example. It has a specific feature that every passenger is able, by means of a personal remote control console, to access the choice of a TV program or play computer games on a general display. Hardware analysis and an example of interface are given.</p>
